dc_title_s: Emergency Response Districts Marathon County, WI 2021
dc_description_s: This data represents emergency response districts for Marathon County, Wisconsin in 2021 and includes the layers 'ems_districts' and 'first_responder_districts'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://www.co.marathon.wi.us/Departments/ConservationPlanningZoning/GEOServices/GeographicInformationSystem(GIS)/GISData.aspx
